Organics/ Wolfblade:
 
"Okay.  Be careful," the valkyrie said, sipping from her mug and turned to the others.
"I don't know about anyone missing, I've been offline for a while."
 
Wolfblade emained still, scowling at the wall with tears running down her face.  Was Malice really worth all of this trouble?  All this spark ache over a male?  She couldn't understand it, and she gave up trying as she heard footsteps approaching the door.
